S|# Cross-Venture Shared Design Rules|> LONG-TERM. Rules that apply to ALL ventures and the YVON dashboard itself. // > vtr-specific overrides → docs/ventures/[name]/DESIGN.md (those files win). // > Schema: each rule must have [added: YYYY-MM-DD]. Rules without dates are invalid. // > 🔴 CRITICAL · 🟡 IMPORTANT · 🟢 GUIDANCE // ---
S|How This File Fits|``` // docs/mem/design.md          ← you are here (shared, all ventures) // docs/ventures/yvon-dashboard/DESIGN.md   ← YVON OS glass system (canonical) // docs/ventures/novizio/DESIGN.md          ← Novizio editorial palette // docs/ventures/hourbour/DESIGN.md         ← Hourbour SaaS palette // ``` // **Override priority:** vtr DESIGN.md > this file > agt mem.md // ---
S|🔴 CRITICAL|- [added: 2026-03-01] No hardcoded hex values anywhere in component files — all color values must trace back to a CSS variable token in `globals.css`. // - [added: 2026-03-01] `globals.css` ↔ `tailwind.config.ts` must stay in sync. If you add a token to one, add it to both immediately. // - [added: 2026-04-19] Minimum readable text: **12px / font-weight 800**. Never below either threshold. // - [added: 2026-04-19] Never apply a dark overlay on top of a light background image. It destroys the pal
S|🟡 IMPORTANT|- [added: 2026-03-01] `mark components 'use client' only when using hooks, browser APIs, or event handlers` — RSC by default. // - [added: 2026-04-19] Every scrollable list that can grow needs: `maxHeight: 360–420px` + `overflowY: auto` + `scrollbarWidth: thin`. No unbounded height. // - [added: 2026-04-19] Each list item gets its own glass card — no shared container wrapping rows in a list. // - [added: 2026-04-19] No drop shadows between stacked cards (no `0 18px 50px` box-shadow between sibli
S|🟢 GUIDANCE|- [added: 2026-03-01] Prefer CSS variable tokens for spacing and radius values too — not just colors. Keeps theming possible. // - [added: 2026-04-19] Dark pill elements (tickers, tab strips, chips on light background): `background: rgba(8,16,36,0.58)`. // - [added: 2026-04-19] KPI metric cards: individual cards per metric (not a combined strip). Each card with its own sparkline if applicable. // - [added: 2026-05-14] If a design token doesn't exist in `globals.css` yet, add it there first — the
S|Shared Font Stack|```css // font-family: 'SF Pro Display', 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; // ``` // SF Pro Display is loaded via `@font-face` in `globals.css` from `/public/fonts/SFPRODISPLAY*.OTF`. This font stack applies to all ventures hosted on YVON. // ---
S|NavBar — Shared Behaviour|The `.glass-nav` CSS class (frosted white pill) is shared across all screens and ventures. // - Text inside: always dark navy `#0c2c52` // - Never `text-white` inside the nav // - Source: `app/components/Nav/NavBar.tsx` // ---
S|Glass System Source of Truth|The canonical glass implementation lives in `app/screens/ceo-command-dashboard/_overview.tsx`. // The documented glass spec lives in `docs/ventures/yvon-dashboard/DESIGN.md`. // If a vtr needs a different visual system, its own DESIGN.md overrides — but the `globals.css` token convention and the 12px/800 floor still apply universally. // ---
S|Never Again (cross-venture)|- [added: 2026-04-19] Applied dark overlay on a light background image across a screen → destroyed glass palette. Rule: no rgba overlay on any background image. // - [added: 2026-03-01] Drift between `globals.css` and `tailwind.config.ts` — tokens existed in one but not the other, causing class mismatches in build. Rule: always update both files together.